THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS
======================

This software incorporates the following third-party components:

1. SpiceSharp
   -----------
   This software uses SpiceSharp, a circuit simulation library.
   SpiceSharp is provided under a liberal open-source license (MIT/BSD-style).
   Copyright and license information for SpiceSharp can be found at:
   https://github.com/SpiceSharp/SpiceSharp

2. KiCad Spice Library Models
   ----------------------------
   This software includes SPICE models from the KiCad Spice Library as a
   courtesy. These models are provided under the GNU General Public License
   version 3 (GPL-3.0).

   The KiCad Spice Library models are included for convenience and are
   subject to the GPL-3.0 license terms. For the full GPL-3.0 license text,
   see the LICENSE file in the archive/third-party-libraries/KiCad-Spice-Library-master/
   directory, or visit: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html

   Note: The inclusion of GPL-3.0 licensed models does not affect the
   licensing of the SpiceService software itself, as these are separate
   components distributed together.

